short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Random Inspirational Quotes On Each New Tab

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
inspiredTab is a chrome extension that replaces the default chrome new tab with a beautiful page that shows inspirational/motivational quotes when you open a new tab to increase your productivity and boost your day. 

- Main Features:
Random inspirational Quotes on each new tab
Random inspirational Background with each quote
Save Quotes
View saved quotes
